Courses
Home / Courses

WECLOUDDATA PROGRAMS

WeCloudData will help develop your professional skills with our selection of Data Science courses. These courses will help you build your Data Science skill set with programs such as Python, SQL, Machine Learning, Big Data, and Deep Learning. Get hands-on with these data science tools, build a strong data project portfolio, and lead you to be hired as a Data Scientist!



Cloud Computing

The cloud computing program is designed for developers and engineers who want to master cloud computing platforms such as AWS, Microsoft Azure, and Google GCP and become certified cloud architect and big data professionals.

View Courses

Data Analytics

Achieve Data Analytics with data flow, data preparation, data visualization, and much more using Excel, SQL, Tableau, and R to apply towards an end-to-end data project.

View Courses

Data Engineering

Master cloud computing, real-time analytics, big data, and ETL to become an expert Data Engineer.

View Courses

Data Fundamentals

Acquire the fundamental data science skills to begin your career in Data Analytics and Data Science.

View Courses

Data Science

Strengthen your Python, Machine Learning, Hadoop, and Spark skills with our seasoned data scientists from famous data-driven companies in Canada.

View Courses



WeCloudData is the leading data science education and career service provider in Canada. Our expert team of data analysts and scientists specializes in preparing individuals and companies with the tools, knowledge, and insights that will help them advance their skills and careers, take charge of their analytics, and leverage the power of data to solve complex business problems.
